description: Chopping Block is changing how Jersey City eats, with every nutritious yet incredibly delicious meal they’re serving. Using only the highest quality organic and natural ingredients, their eclectic menu exclusively features items that your body will appreciate just as much as your taste buds. Inspired by Jamaican, Italian, and American cuisines, you’re invited to enjoy dishes like Jerk Chicken, Ackee & Saltfish with Fried Dumplings, 100% Jamaica Blue Mountain Coffee, and much more. It’s no wonder why this truck, with its emphasis on promoting whole wellness while providing full flavors, is a local foodie favorite.For your next meal, feed your soul, fuel your body, choose health, choose Chopping Block.
name: Chopping Block
